ankeleiqi_2.value: Anchorage wants to draw... what I dreamed of above the clouds

nengdai_1.value: Are you the only one who can see this?

nengdai_1_1_1.value: Good. Then I will share my daily activities with you from now on. I just hope it doesn't bore you...

nengdai_1_2.value: I'm happy to have something so lovely all to myself.

nengdai_1_2_1.value: Really... If you came over every day, you could have even more, don't you think?

tianlangxing_1.value: Maids live to satisfy their masters, so I have taken the liberty of learning new skills for the sake of better serving my honourable Master.

tianlangxing_1_1.value: I hope I can satisfy you, too, Sirius.

tianlangxing_1_1_1.value: Do you really mean that, Master? Then please allow me to use all that I've learned to serve you!

tianlangxing_1_2_1.value: Yes! Very useful ones that will help bind us together forever!
